{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2054020/extras/veilendor_logo_chrystal_v3.png?t=1718819091\" /><br>Light of Veilendor is a third-person action adventure game in which the main character you play is a mighty crystal wolf from an ancient wolf clan descended from the first gods. The wolf has several skills and powers that you learn more about and will be able to use during the game, where you have to explore and follow the clues that unfold through the narrative.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2054020/extras/LOV_Clip1_Runes_Optim.gif?t=1718819091\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Explore the world of Veilendor</strong></h2>Travel through thrilling landscapes on your epic quest to overthrow the lord of darkness, Gotarath. While various magical animals and creatures roam this world and offer their own challenges, the evil nightmare monsters lurk in the shadows, ready to attack.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2054020/extras/LOV_Clip2_Runes_Optim.gif?t=1718819091\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Unlock special abilities as the story unfolds</strong></h2>To learn more about the story and to unlock the wolf's magical abilities, you must collect various items along the way.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2054020/extras/LOV_Clip3_Runes_Optim.gif?t=1718819091\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Note</strong></h2>Light of Veilendor is in an early stage of development, which means that the images shown here are subject to change. Follow the game development on our Discord server!","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2054020/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1718819091","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/205